item.title: Wild Area - Safe Area - Entrana
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

Go into client.java and search nonwild something should come up and under there will be a whole bunch of points that look like this || (absX >= 3237 && absX <=3247 && absY >= 3512 && absY <=3247 ) || (absX >= 3239 && absX <= 3247 && absY >= 3513 && absY <=3521 ) || this is just and example well at the end of one of them copy and past this || (absX >= xxx1 && absX <=xxx2 && absY >= yyy1 && absY <=yyy2 )

Now imagine you making a box around the island in xxx1 put the lowest x cord and in xxx2 put the highest x cord and in yyy1 put the lowst y cord and in yyy2 put the highest y cord hope this helped
